channel.title: My port 80 is blocked when making a HighScores. How to unblock it?
channel.description:
I created an HighScores with the TuT of Creating HighScores link fixed 100%. I did everything right and it work but I need players on my HighScores. So I needed to portforward port 80 so I did it but nothing changed. I either unblock it in my FireWall and it didn't work. I would like to know how to open my port 80 now ? Or players cannot be on it and I really want my HighScores to work.
Thank you very much if you help.
